Here are the 7 concepts and everything under each one:
1. API Design
REST, gRPC, idempotency, pagination, versioning, retries, error handling
2. Databases
SQL, indexing, transactions, query tuning, replication, partitioning, consistency tradeoffs
3. Caching
Redis, cache invalidation, TTL strategy, read-through vs write-through, hot keys, consistency risks
4. Async Systems
Queues, Kafka, retries, backoff, dead letter queues, idempotent consumers, eventual consistency
5. Distributed Systems Basics
Load balancing, sharding, leader-follower replication, service discovery, fault tolerance, CAP tradeoffs
6. Reliability and Observability
Logs, metrics, tracing, alerts, SLOs, incident handling, debugging production issues
7. Architecture and Tradeoffs
Monolith vs microservices, consistency vs availability, performance vs cost, simplicity vs flexibility
